pipeline "Windows Server"
stage 0 match either
rule "Mega winlog field rename"
stage 1 match either
rule "Application Drop Events"
rule "Defender drop events"
rule "RDP drop events 1"
rule "RDP drop events 2"
rule "Security drop events"
rule "WMI drop events "
rule "WinRM drop events"
rule "TaskScheduler Drop events"
rule "System drop events"
stage 2 match either
rule "Defender Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "RDP Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "Task Scheduler Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "Windows Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "Winrm Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "WMI Log Event Id Enrichment"
end

pipeline "PowerShell"
stage 0 match either
rule "PowerShell drop events"
stage 1 match either
rule "PowerShell Encrichment"
end

rule "Sysmon Extract RuleName Field"
when
  has_field("RuleName")
then
    set_fields(
        fields:
            key_value(
                value: to_string($message.RuleName),
                trim_value_chars: "",
                trim_key_chars:"",
                delimiters: ",",
                kv_delimiters: "="
            ),
            prefix: "Mitre"
        );
end

description.@value: Pipeline to process Windows Sysmon Events

source.@value:
pipeline "Sysmon"
stage 1 match either
rule "Sysmon Log Event Id Enrichment"
rule "Sysmon Extract RuleName Field"
stage 0 match either
rule "Mega winlog field rename"
end

rule "RDP drop events 1"
when
  to_string($message.Channel) == "Microsoft-Windows-TerminalServices-RemoteConnectionManager/Operational"
  AND NOT
  (
  to_string($message.EventId) != "1149" 
  ) 
then
    drop_message();
end

rule "WinRM drop events"
when
  to_string($message.Channel) == "Microsoft-Windows-WinRM/Operational"
  AND NOT
  (
  to_string($message.EventId) == "6" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "8" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "15" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "16" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "33" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "81" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "82" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "19" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "134" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "168" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "169"
  )
then
    drop_message();
end

rule "Drop log sources"
when
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Application" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "System" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Security" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-TerminalServices-LocalSessionManager/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "icrosoft-Windows-TerminalServices-RemoteConnectionManager/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-PowerShell/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-Windows Defender/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-TaskScheduler/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-WMI-Activity/Operational" OR
  to_string($message.Channel) != "Microsoft-Windows-WinRM/Operational" 
then
  drop_message();
end

rule "System drop events"
when
  to_string($message.Channel) == "System" 
  AND NOT
  (
  to_string($message.EventId) == "6" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "19" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "104" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "1125" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "1126" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "1129" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7000" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7024" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7032" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7033" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7034" OR
  to_string($message.EventId) == "7045" 
  )
then
    drop_message();
end

rule "WMI Log Event Id Enrichment"

when
	to_string($message.Channel) == "Microsoft-Windows-WMI-Activity/Operational"
then
	set_field("WmiEventName", lookup_value("wmi", $message.EventId));
	set_field("DfirEvent","true");
end

rule "Stage Bypass"

when
    has_field("timetsamp")
then
end
